  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK729">
<l>kallā tavariṉ kaṭaiyeṉpa kaṟṟaṟintu</l>
<l>nallā ravaiyañcu vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They who, though they have learned and understood, are yet afraid of the assembly of the good, are said to be inferior (even) to the illiterate.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
